Learn these as Android Engineer:

📱 UI & Jetpack
* Jetpack Compose (Modern UI toolkit)
* Material Design Components
* Navigation Component
* ConstraintLayout
* ViewBinding/DataBinding
* Fragment
* Lifecycle Components
* Paging 3
* SwipeRefreshLayout

🌐 Network & API
* Retrofit (REST client)
* OkHttp (HTTP client)
* Ktor (Kotlin-first HTTP client)
* Websocket
* gRPC

💾 Data & Serialization
* Kotlin Serialization
* Moshi (Modern JSON library)
* Gson (JSON parsing)
* Protocol Buffers

🖼️ Image Loading & Media
* Coil (Kotlin-first image loading)
* Glide (Image loading)
* ExoPlayer (Video/Audio)
* CameraX
* MediaStore
* Okio (I/O operations)

⚡ Background Processing
* Coroutines & Flow
* WorkManager (Background tasks)
* Background Services
* App Startup
* Foreground Services

💽 Local Storage
* Room (SQLite abstraction)
* DataStore (Key-Value storage)
* SQLDelight (SQL toolkit)
* Realm Database
* Store (Repository pattern)
* SharedPreferences (Legacy)

💉 Dependency Injection
* Hilt (Recommended DI)
* Koin (Lightweight DI)
* Dagger 2
* Kodein

📊 Logging & Monitoring
* Timber (Logging)
* Napier (Multiplatform logging)
* Crashlytics (Crash reporting)
* LeakCanary (Memory leak detection)
* Sentry (Error tracking)
* Firebase Performance
* NewRelic (Performance monitoring)

🧪 Testing
* JUnit (Unit testing)
* Mockk (Kotlin mocking)
* Espresso (UI testing)
* Robolectric (Unit testing)
* Compose UI Testing
* Turbine (Flow testing)
* Kotest (Testing framework)
* Truth (Assertions)

🛠️ Development Tools
* Ktlint (Kotlin linter)
* Detekt (Static code analysis)
* Gradle (Build tool)
* R8/ProGuard (Code shrinking)
* Android Studio
* Konsist (Architecture linting)

🚀 CI/CD
* GitHub Actions
* CircleCI
* Fastlane
* Firebase App Distribution
* Google Play Console

📈 Analytics & Monitoring
* Firebase Analytics
* Mixpanel
* Tealium
* AppsFlyer
* Google Analytics
* Firebase Crashlytics

🔒 Security
* Biometric
* Encrypted SharedPreferences
* Android Keystore
* Certificate Pinning
* ProGuard/R8
